# TabletopInteraction.DirectPickupBehavior.CollisionResolutionBehavior.disabled

**Case**

Use this value to disable collision resolution.

## Declaration

```swift
case disabled
```

## Resolution behaviors

- **TabletopInteraction.DirectPickupBehavior.CollisionResolutionBehavior.automatic**: The automatic behavior moves and rotates the object to ensure that it does not penetrate the collision targets.
